resource_name.description: The name of the resource to create.

api_version.description: The API version to use for the operation.

parameters.description: Parameters for creating or updating the resource.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group for the resource. The name is case insensitive.

resource_provider_namespace.description: The namespace of the resource provider.

resource_type.description: The resource type of the resource to create.

subscription_id.description: The ID of the target subscription.
